# mhr-b2b-client-java (Java 11 / Jakarta)

My Health Record **PCEHR B2B** client — **not** Healthcare Identifiers (HI). Do **not** reference **`myhr-b2b-client-java`** or other aggregator/unified client projects in docs or comments. End-user docs: **`README.md`**, **`ADHA-THIRD-PARTY-SCOPE.md`**, **`MAINTAINERS.md`**. Agent WSDL/facade matrix: **`.cursor/WSDL-CLIENT-PURPOSES.md`** (gitignored).

## Release line (integrator docs use Maven Central versions only)

| Version | Java | APIs | Facades |
| ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |
| **1.7.0** | 11 | Jakarta | **26** (full WSDL line) |

**This checkout:** **`1.7.0-SNAPSHOT`** — **`au.gov.nehta:pcehr-compiled-wsdl`** at **`${project.version}`**; Java **11** / **`jakarta.*`** XML APIs.

## WSDL/XSD (committed in Git)

PCEHR B2B WSDL/XSD under `wsdls/src/main/resources/` are **not** separate ADHA-licensed artefacts (unlike HI in hi-b2b-client-java). **Keep them in Git** for reference and for **`pcehr-compiled-wsdl-java`**. Compile against **`au.gov.nehta:pcehr-compiled-wsdl`** at **`pcehr.wsdl.version`** = **`${project.version}`** — install matching **`pcehr-compiled-wsdl-java`** first. **Six** view facades under `clients.view`; seven **`getView`** types — **`ADHA-THIRD-PARTY-SCOPE.md`**. Optional **`-Pwsimport`**: in-repo wsimport validation.

## Build

- JDK **11**: install sibling **`pcehr-compiled-wsdl-java`** at the same version, then `mvn -B "-Dgpg.skip=true" clean verify`
- WSDL validation: `mvn -B "-Dgpg.skip=true" -Pwsimport clean verify`
- JAX-WS: **`com.sun.xml.ws:jaxws-rt` 4.0.4** — not legacy Metro **`webservices-*`**
- Enforcer bans Metro **`webservices-*`** and **`javax.*`** XML API coordinates (test-scoped **`jaxb-api`** excepted for legacy NEHTA fixtures)
- Default Surefire: offline tests; **`-Pintegration`** for mutual-TLS suite
- Strict Javadoc: **`doclint=all`**, **`failOnWarnings=true`**

See `README.md`, `MAINTAINERS.md`, `wsdls/readme.txt`.
